 Task Overview:The task was to design a web page dedicated to someone I admire, incorporating text, images, and a visually appealing layout.
 
 My Approach & Solution:
Designing the Structure:-
Used HTML to structure the page with sections for introduction, biography, images, and quotes.
Added appropriate paragraphs to provide a comprehensive narrative about the person.
Styling the Page:-
Utilized CSS to style the text with different font styles to make the content engaging.
Applied background colors and images to enhance the visual appeal.
Used CSS Flexbox and Grid for a responsive and well-aligned layout.

Results & Learnings:
Successfully built a visually appealing and informative tribute page.
Enhanced my skills in HTML structuring and CSS styling.
Learned to create responsive layouts using CSS Flexbox and Grid.

